========= Passives =========
Distress Spores: When the myconid takes damage, all other myconids within 240 ft of it can sense its pain
Sun Sickness: While in sunlight, the myconid has disadvantage on ability checks, attack rolls, and saving throws. The myconid dies if it spends more than 1 hour in direct sunlight
Rapport Spores: As an action, a 20-ft radius cloud of spores extends for the myconid. These spores can go around corners and ffect only creatures with an Intelligence of 2 or higher that aren't undead, constructs, or elementals. Affected creatrues can communicate telepathically with one or another while they are within 30 ft of each other. The effect lasts for 1 hour
